name: Alex Stalart
markerNotes: The Spotify bio states: "The vocals in my tracks are generated by artificial intelligence." Since emerging in 2025, the artist has released numerous singles and albums. The Instagram account is mostly in Russian, featuring AI-generated images unrelated to the artist, with no other public presence.
